author: USA TODAY, Anika Reed, USA TODAY
title: Queen interacted with Boris Johnson, Charles; palace silent on if she's had COVID-19 test
description: Queen Elizabeth "remains in good health" despite meeting just weeks ago with Boris Johnson, who tested positive for coronavirus .
